<h4>
<img src="Themes/celeste/images/useroff.gif" alt="离线"/>
<a href="?PHPSESSID=608b062285b07a8dd1e4c54d0838ba14&amp;action=profile;u=2590" title="检视会员资料:  AlbertNi">AlbertNi</a>
</h4>
